00:28:36,860 --> 00:28:39,500
Some wanted autographs, manuscripts

562
00:28:39,500 --> 00:28:40,550
and also extra volumes.

563
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:19,870
Chu Li.

564
00:29:20,190 --> 00:29:21,510
Come take a look.

565
00:29:22,910 --> 00:29:25,380
What do you think
about this publicity banner?

566
00:29:25,580 --> 00:29:27,120
[An oriental fantasy masterpiece
from best selling author Zhou Chuan]

567
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:28,220
[Book of Luo He God]

568
00:29:27,580 --> 00:29:28,790
It's good.

569
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:29,750
Good.

570
00:29:55,030 --> 00:29:55,950
Hello?

571
00:29:55,950 --> 00:29:56,630
Chief Editor Yu.

572
00:29:56,630 --> 00:29:57,790
It's me, Zhou Chuan.

573
00:29:57,790 --> 00:29:58,820
Hi, Mr Zhou Chuan.

574
00:29:58,820 --> 00:29:59,670
Can I help you?

575
00:30:01,110 --> 00:30:02,230
I just want to know.

576
00:30:02,230 --> 00:30:03,910
I've been trying to call my editor

577
00:30:03,910 --> 00:30:05,870
about the online pre-sales of my book

578
00:30:05,870 --> 00:30:07,350
but I didn't get any response.

579
00:30:07,350 --> 00:30:08,230
Is she alive?

580
00:30:10,910 --> 00:30:13,110
Mr Zhou Chuan,
your managing editor

581
00:30:13,110 --> 00:30:14,310
is still alive.

582
00:30:14,550 --> 00:30:16,750
[Online pre-sales is going well.
Please don't worry.]

583
00:30:17,230 --> 00:30:17,990
[Chu Li]

584
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:19,590
[must have been exhausted.]

585
00:30:19,990 --> 00:30:20,820
I'll remind her

586
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:21,700
to check her phone.

587
00:30:22,070 --> 00:30:23,580
I'm glad the online pre-sales
is going well.

588
00:30:23,580 --> 00:30:25,190
All good now. Bye.

589
00:30:34,390 --> 00:30:35,110
Chu Li.

590
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:37,550
Chief Editor.
Do you need anything?

591
00:30:37,710 --> 00:30:38,790
You must be tired.

592
00:30:39,230 --> 00:30:41,180
The online pre-sales is going well.

593
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:42,230
You've worked hard.

594
00:30:42,230 --> 00:30:43,390
Thanks, Chief Editor.

595
00:30:43,820 --> 00:30:45,630
You and Ah Xiang can go home now.

596
00:30:45,630 --> 00:30:46,830
Take a good rest.

597
00:30:48,340 --> 00:30:50,230
Oh, right.
You'd better check your phone.

598
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:54,820
[The subway is closed.]

599
00:30:54,460 --> 00:31:06,520
[Not Drama King, it's Saviour]

600
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:56,150
[Mr Zhou Chuan is hungry.]

601
00:30:56,150 --> 00:30:57,950
[You probably need
to take a cab home tonight.]

602
00:30:57,950 --> 00:30:59,110
[An additional fee is incurred
if you take a cab at this hour.]

603
00:30:59,110 --> 00:31:00,150
[You're still in the office?]

604
00:31:00,150 --> 00:31:01,150
[Are you still working
on the online pre-sales?]

605
00:31:01,150 --> 00:31:02,790
[Your risk of sudden death is increasing.]

606
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:04,110
[You have a nice bed at home]

607
00:31:04,110 --> 00:31:05,310
[but you rather sleep in the office?]

608
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:06,470
[Are you out of your mind?]

609
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:18,310
Miss.

610
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:19,390
Do you go to gym?

611
00:31:19,390 --> 00:31:20,830
Miss, I can give you a discount.

612
00:31:20,830 --> 00:31:22,030
You don't look fat

613
00:31:22,030 --> 00:31:23,190
but you can still strengthen your body.

614
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:24,230
Our trainers are all award winners.

615
00:31:24,230 --> 00:31:24,830
No, thanks.

616
00:31:24,830 --> 00:31:26,230
Our equipment are very good.

617
00:31:26,230 --> 00:31:26,950
No, thanks.

618
00:31:26,950 --> 00:31:28,390
Look at our facilities.

619
00:31:28,390 --> 00:31:28,820
Look.

620
00:31:29,070 --> 00:31:29,790
Stop pulling me.

621
00:31:29,790 --> 00:31:31,580
Your fee is equivalent to
my monthly meal expenses.

622
00:31:31,580 --> 00:31:32,710
Let me go.

623
00:31:34,390 --> 00:31:35,310
I'm sorry.

624
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:36,630
Why are you so rude?

625
00:31:36,630 --> 00:31:37,390
Just tell me if you're not interested.

626
00:31:37,390 --> 00:31:38,620
Why did you push me?

627
00:31:38,620 --> 00:31:39,940
You used violence on me.

628
00:31:40,150 --> 00:31:41,230
You have to compensate me.

629
00:31:41,990 --> 00:31:43,590
Compensate?

630
00:31:43,870 --> 00:31:44,830
These papers

631
00:31:44,830 --> 00:31:45,870
probably cost 20 yuan.

632
00:31:45,870 --> 00:31:48,030
Do you want me to print a few hundred more
to build you a shelter?

633
00:31:48,030 --> 00:31:49,060
These are colour prints.

634
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:50,310
It costs me one and a half
for one piece of paper.

635
00:31:50,470 --> 00:31:51,150
So many pieces here.

636
00:31:51,150 --> 00:31:52,550
You have to pay me 300 yuan.

637
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:53,510
If not, I'll call the cops.

638
00:31:53,510 --> 00:31:54,790
300 yuan?

639
00:31:55,390 --> 00:31:56,590
Call the cops then.

640
00:31:56,590 --> 00:31:58,590
I can sue you for extortion or something.

641
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:00,550
You...

642
00:32:00,550 --> 00:32:01,310
Don't run.

643
00:32:01,310 --> 00:32:02,310
You can't go if you don't pay.

644
00:32:02,310 --> 00:32:03,260
Stop pulling me.

645
00:32:03,260 --> 00:32:04,350
Compensate me first.

646
00:32:38,710 --> 00:32:39,870
What's going on?

647
00:32:42,310 --> 00:32:42,950
Get up.

648
00:32:46,350 --> 00:32:47,230
I'm scared

649
00:32:47,230 --> 00:32:48,070
just because you have company.

650
00:32:48,070 --> 00:32:49,390
You still have to compensate me.

651
00:32:49,670 --> 00:32:50,430
Compensate...

652
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:52,350
He hit him.

653
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,150
He hit him.

654
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:01,830
Don't act on impulse in future.

655
00:33:01,830 --> 00:33:04,350
Although the other party started it,

656
00:33:04,350 --> 00:33:05,790
using violence in public

657
00:33:05,790 --> 00:33:07,470
is still wrong.

658
00:33:08,230 --> 00:33:08,940
We got it.

659
00:33:08,940 --> 00:33:10,590
Thank you, Mr Policeman.

660
00:33:25,670 --> 00:33:26,220
Get on.

661
00:33:27,510 --> 00:33:28,150
I'll carry you on my back.

662
00:33:29,710 --> 00:33:30,270
What?

663
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:31,230
Did you hurt your head too?

664
00:33:31,230 --> 00:33:32,590
I said I'll carry you on my back.

665
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:33,990
Did I not make myself clear?

666
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:37,950
But...

667
00:33:51,950 --> 00:33:52,950
What is it now?

668
00:33:52,950 --> 00:33:53,990
Can you hurry up?

669
00:33:54,270 --> 00:33:56,790
Don't let me squat here
in front of the police station.

670
00:34:06,350 --> 00:34:07,590
About that...

671
00:34:07,590 --> 00:34:09,949
The online pre-sales is almost ready.

672
00:34:09,949 --> 00:34:12,750
We are just waiting for web support now.

673
00:34:12,750 --> 00:34:14,550
The circulation department
is working on it already.

674
00:34:17,469 --> 00:34:19,139
For the exclusive giveaways,

675
00:34:19,460 --> 00:34:21,030
what do you think we should give?

676
00:34:21,030 --> 00:34:22,150
Autograph?

677
00:34:22,150 --> 00:34:24,830
Autograph might not be that attractive.

678
00:34:25,550 --> 00:34:26,830
Not attractive?

679
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:31,150
How about lucky draw for forwarded post?

680
00:34:31,150 --> 00:34:32,949
This is very important.

681
00:34:33,780 --> 00:34:35,420
Do you have any private item?

682
00:34:38,270 --> 00:34:39,830
Private item?

683
00:34:42,989 --> 00:34:44,469
My editor's head.

684
00:34:53,140 --> 00:34:54,710
Oh, right. Mr Zhou Chuan.

685
00:34:54,990 --> 00:34:57,150
Why were you on the street today?

686
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:59,230
You weren't even walking the dog.

687
00:35:00,590 --> 00:35:01,750
I was on my way

688
00:35:01,750 --> 00:35:02,700
to the convenience store.

689
00:35:03,260 --> 00:35:04,270
Nothing odd about that.

690
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:13,820
Why don't we take a cab...

691
00:35:44,470 --> 00:35:46,590
[Chu Li, don't forget our appointment]

692
00:35:44,810 --> 00:35:49,520
[Flying Elephant]

693
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:48,260
[with the printing house
tomorrow evening.]

694
00:35:54,490 --> 00:35:59,770
[Flying Elephant]

695
00:35:55,710 --> 00:35:57,430
[I won't go the office tomorrow morning.]

696
00:35:57,430 --> 00:35:59,030
[Mr Zhou Chuan wants to
have a meeting with me]

697
00:35:59,030 --> 00:36:00,630
[about the exclusive giveaways.]

698
00:35:59,770 --> 00:36:00,650
[Chu Li]

699
00:36:03,270 --> 00:36:04,150
Get up.

700
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:05,790
Disinfect your wound before you sleep.

701
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:07,230
You'll get an infection if you don't.

702
00:36:13,430 --> 00:36:14,660
If you don't get up now,

703
00:36:14,660 --> 00:36:16,670
I'll pull out your pants.

704
00:36:18,950 --> 00:36:21,230
Don't think that you can get away

705
00:36:21,230 --> 00:36:22,550
with your good looks and writing skills.

706
00:36:22,550 --> 00:36:24,670
I'll call the cops

707
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:27,310
if you do something to me when I'm asleep.

708
00:36:28,590 --> 00:36:29,790
I just want you to get up

709
00:36:29,790 --> 00:36:31,670
and take off your pants.

710
00:36:33,670 --> 00:36:35,270
What?

711
00:36:35,270 --> 00:36:36,630
You have to disinfect that knee.

712
00:36:36,630 --> 00:36:38,100
You have been out all day.

713
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,350
Are you going to fall asleep
with all that?

714
00:36:40,670 --> 00:36:42,060
Alright, I got it.

715
00:36:42,060 --> 00:36:43,590
I can't take off my pants with you here.

716
00:36:43,590 --> 00:36:45,030
Go downstairs now.

717
00:36:45,030 --> 00:36:46,670
I'll take them off once you're gone.

718
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:49,390
You can't fool me with that.

719
00:36:49,390 --> 00:36:50,470
It's a trick to get me out

720
00:36:50,470 --> 00:36:51,550
so that you can continue sleeping,
isn't it?

721
00:36:51,550 --> 00:36:52,390
No, no.

722
00:36:52,390 --> 00:36:54,030
You go out first. I'll take them off.

723
00:36:54,430 --> 00:36:55,350
Alright?

724
00:36:56,310 --> 00:36:57,430
I'll come up to check in a while.

725
00:36:58,750 --> 00:37:00,070
You sound like

726
00:37:00,070 --> 00:37:01,150
a teacher

727
00:37:01,150 --> 00:37:03,180
checking on a student's homework.

728
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:04,470
Go now.

729
00:37:16,940 --> 00:37:17,550
Hello?

730
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:18,630
Buddy.

731
00:37:21,910 --> 00:37:24,070
What got into you?

732
00:37:24,070 --> 00:37:25,430
I'm not used to this.

733
00:37:25,430 --> 00:37:26,150
What's the matter?

734
00:37:26,430 --> 00:37:28,230
I think I'm undergoing puberty.

735
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:30,550
What happened?

736
00:37:31,950 --> 00:37:33,910
I suddenly realize
the deep physical meaning

737
00:37:33,910 --> 00:37:36,230
in gender distinction of mankind.

738
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:37,510
Man

739
00:37:38,710 --> 00:37:39,870
and woman.

740
00:37:39,870 --> 00:37:41,790
I don't understand.

741
00:37:41,790 --> 00:37:43,630
It's tiring to explain to you.

742
00:37:46,830 --> 00:37:48,070
Go downstairs to apply medicine

743
00:37:48,070 --> 00:37:49,670
and come back up to bed.

744
00:37:50,110 --> 00:37:51,070
You can sleep in tomorrow.

745
00:37:51,070 --> 00:37:52,190
I've applied leave for you.

746
00:37:52,190 --> 00:37:54,460
Just go to the printing house
in the evening.

747
00:37:55,510 --> 00:37:57,470
Why are you fixing my schedule?

748
00:37:58,860 --> 00:38:00,230
Flying Elephant texted you.

749
00:38:00,670 --> 00:38:02,310
You looked at my phone?

750
00:38:02,790 --> 00:38:04,630
The message popped up
according to your setting.

751
00:38:04,630 --> 00:38:06,150
I can't unseen it.

752
00:38:06,630 --> 00:38:07,710
Since I've seen it,

753
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:09,310
I decided to apply leave for you.

754
00:38:09,310 --> 00:38:10,150
What's the problem?

755
00:38:11,430 --> 00:38:13,700
This did sound like me.

756
00:38:14,430 --> 00:38:15,750
I guessed it right.

757
00:38:15,750 --> 00:38:16,510
You

758
00:38:16,510 --> 00:38:18,470
always talk behind my back
with your colleagues.

759
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:20,270
"Mr Zhou Chuan is running late again."

760
00:38:20,270 --> 00:38:21,670
"Who does he think he is?"

761
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:22,940
"The centre of the universe?"

762
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:26,350
You added that last one.

763
00:38:29,630 --> 00:38:30,750
Your leg.

764
00:38:36,910 --> 00:38:38,030
Stop jumping.

765
00:38:38,030 --> 00:38:39,350
The stairs will collapse.

766
00:38:39,350 --> 00:38:41,150
Don't you know you are heavy?

767
00:38:42,420 --> 00:38:43,670
I must thank you for your trouble

768
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:46,030
to carry me home then.

769
00:38:46,380 --> 00:38:47,470
I'm glad you know.

770
00:38:50,510 --> 00:38:51,510
Get on.

771
00:38:53,190 --> 00:38:55,150
Since I've started a good deed,
let me carry you down.

772
00:38:57,500 --> 00:38:58,990
Thank you, Mr Zhou Chuan.

773
00:39:04,540 --> 00:39:05,670
Go slow.

774
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:07,270
You pulled an all nighter

775
00:39:07,270 --> 00:39:08,310
just for that 350 thousand.

776
00:39:10,030 --> 00:39:11,390
If you don't hit that target,

777
00:39:11,390 --> 00:39:13,390
you have to carry me
around the neighbourhood.

778
00:39:13,780 --> 00:39:14,750
I don't want to.

779
00:39:16,590 --> 00:39:17,830
Be gentle.

780
00:39:33,350 --> 00:39:34,750
Are you making some embroidery?

781
00:39:35,550 --> 00:39:36,270
At this rate,

782
00:39:36,270 --> 00:39:37,660
it will take you forever.

783
00:39:38,390 --> 00:39:39,230
Let me do it.

784
00:39:39,950 --> 00:39:41,670
You know how to treat wounds?

785
00:39:51,620 --> 00:39:52,750
I attended first aid training.

786
00:39:56,790 --> 00:39:58,830
Thank you, Mr Zhou Chuan.

787
00:39:59,310 --> 00:40:00,590
You really don't want to slit the wound

788
00:40:00,590 --> 00:40:01,990
to check for residues?

789
00:40:02,350 --> 00:40:04,030
What if the wound heals

790
00:40:04,030 --> 00:40:05,310
with the residue still inside?

791
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:09,830
Let me do it myself.

792
00:40:30,580 --> 00:40:31,710
Eight Treasure Congee?

793
00:40:38,940 --> 00:40:40,670
Why is it so salty?

794
00:40:42,870 --> 00:40:43,950
Mr Zhou Chuan.

795
00:40:43,950 --> 00:40:44,790
I'm really sorry

796
00:40:44,790 --> 00:40:45,950
I got up late this morning

797
00:40:45,950 --> 00:40:47,510
and did not make you breakfast.

798
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:48,180
Oh, right.

799
00:40:48,180 --> 00:40:49,670
Give me the phone number
of this take-out restaurant.

800
00:40:49,670 --> 00:40:50,990
I want to file a complaint.

801
00:40:50,990 --> 00:40:52,700
Food has dignity too.

802
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:54,110
This Eight Treasure Congee
is supposed to be sweet.

803
00:40:54,110 --> 00:40:55,910
This is salty and inedible.

804
00:40:56,190 --> 00:40:57,070
I made this.

805
00:40:58,790 --> 00:40:59,950
You made this?

806
00:41:08,750 --> 00:41:10,830
Actually, it won't be salty

807
00:41:10,830 --> 00:41:12,630
after adding hot water.

808
00:41:14,910 --> 00:41:16,190
Then you should have more.

809
00:41:17,110 --> 00:41:18,950
Eight Treasure Congee can boost your qi
and nourish your blood.

810
00:41:18,950 --> 00:41:20,950
It's perfect for hard workers like you.

811
00:41:22,070 --> 00:41:25,070
You made this congee just for me?

812
00:41:25,790 --> 00:41:26,750
Yes.

813
00:41:26,750 --> 00:41:28,990
I'm afraid if you work yourself to death,

814
00:41:28,990 --> 00:41:30,390
no one can help me
hit the 350 thousand target.

815
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:34,550
I knew it.

816
00:41:43,990 --> 00:41:45,470
Hello? Chief Editor Yu.

817
00:41:46,470 --> 00:41:47,380
Really?

818
00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:48,790
I'll tell him now.

819
00:41:49,580 --> 00:41:50,870
Good news.

820
00:41:50,870 --> 00:41:52,630
Pre-sales of your book starts next week.

821
00:41:52,870 --> 00:41:55,300
I'll hashtag you
on all official platforms.

822
00:41:55,300 --> 00:41:56,350
You must forward them out.

823
00:41:56,350 --> 00:41:57,910
The more the better.

824
00:41:58,380 --> 00:42:00,030
I'll have to pass this congee.

825
00:42:00,030 --> 00:42:01,270
I need to go to the printing house now.

826
00:42:05,630 --> 00:42:07,670
It's really too salty.

827
00:42:09,550 --> 00:42:11,430
I've booked a cab for you.

828
00:42:11,430 --> 00:42:12,270
I'll pay for it.

829
00:42:18,550 --> 00:42:19,630
Goodbye.
